### ESPN Teams — Men's
# Returns all Men's college basketball teams (name, abbreviation, ESPN ID).
# Used by importSchools() to enrich shortDisplayName and abbreviation.
# Look for the team you want in teams[].team.{id, displayName, shortDisplayName, abbreviation}.

GET https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/basketball/mens-college-basketball/teams?limit=500
Accept: application/json

###

### ESPN Teams — Women's
# Returns all Women's college basketball teams.
# Same structure as Men's.

GET https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/basketball/womens-college-basketball/teams?limit=500
Accept: application/json

